  "\<lbrakk> interfree_aux(None, r, Some a); interfree_aux(None, i, Some a); 
  interfree_aux(Some c, q, Some a)\<rbrakk>\<Longrightarrow> 
  interfree_aux(Some (AnnWhile r b i c), q, Some a)"
apply(simp add: interfree_aux_def)
by force
 
